　　(2) To protect the rights and interests of users and the public in case of emergency;
　　(3) In order to protect the trademark right, patent right and any other legal rights and interests of Apera Instruments;
　　(4) Other cases that require disclosure, editing, or disclosure of personal information;
　　Ltd. has the right to use the user’s personal information in the following (including but not limited to) several cases:
